WEBVTT

00:02.126 --> 00:03.791
So, I got assigned to this one rookie,

00:03.849 --> 00:05.296
and on his training day,

00:05.354 --> 00:08.108
I made him smoke angel dust
at gunpoint.

00:08.544 --> 00:11.786
King Kong ain't got
nothing on me.

00:11.844 --> 00:13.344
Isn't that the plot
and tagline of...

00:13.402 --> 00:15.494
The movie "Training Day"?
Yes, great observation, Tank.

00:15.551 --> 00:16.869
That's because it's based on
my life.

00:16.926 --> 00:19.087
Lunch is over.
Bus your trays.

00:20.136 --> 00:21.876
- Now, Peralta.
- I haven't finished

00:21.948 --> 00:24.803
- my lemon cookie, bull.
- And you're not gonna get to,

00:24.861 --> 00:26.099
either. Give it to me.

00:26.157 --> 00:27.700
Oh, you want the cookie?

00:30.237 --> 00:31.792
- Oh!
- There's your cookie.

00:31.850 --> 00:33.927
- You're going in the hole.
- Oh, I'm going in the hole?

00:33.984 --> 00:35.319
- Yeah.
- Yeah, bring it on!

00:35.377 --> 00:37.046
Jake, Jake, Jake, Jake!

00:37.103 --> 00:38.472
Remember what you saw here today!

00:39.577 --> 00:40.722
You can lock me up,

00:40.749 --> 00:42.089
but one day
I'll get out of here,

00:42.147 --> 00:44.412
and I'll come for you!
I'll come for all of you!

00:44.470 --> 00:45.533
Hey, Warden. What's up?

00:45.591 --> 00:46.724
Next time, don't wait so long

00:46.781 --> 00:48.169
to spit the cookie.
I've been waiting

00:48.226 --> 00:50.068
in here for four
minutes, and it's gross.

00:50.126 --> 00:52.158
- Yeah, it really is.
- Okay, snitch time.

00:52.216 --> 00:54.118
- What's up with Romero?
- All right, he's got

00:54.176 --> 00:56.276
a "delivery" coming in
on Wednesday night.

00:56.334 --> 00:58.505
One of the cafeteria workers
is smuggling something in

00:58.563 --> 01:00.539
- with the produce.
- Great.

01:00.699 --> 01:02.517
- See you Thursday.
- Wait, what?

01:02.575 --> 01:04.486
You're just gonna leave
me in here, in solitary?

01:04.545 --> 01:07.369
You spit in a guard's face.
That's five days in the hole.

01:07.427 --> 01:09.229
Yeah, but, I mean,
you made me do that.

01:09.287 --> 01:11.356
Well, we don't want anybody
getting suspicious, huh?

01:11.430 --> 01:12.596
Have fun.

01:15.310 --> 01:16.845
Try not to go crazy.

01:20.882 --> 01:23.447
Okay.
No big deal.

01:23.644 --> 01:25.648
Five days is nothing.
I'm not afraid to be alone

01:25.706 --> 01:27.205
with my thoughts. My
thoughts are awesome.

01:27.262 --> 01:29.478
"Die Hard 6" on a cruise ship,
pizza bagel restaurant,

01:29.551 --> 01:31.755
my father never loved me, I'm
gonna die alone... oh, boy,

01:31.812 --> 01:33.748
that happened fast.
Guard? Guard!

01:33.848 --> 01:36.795
♪♪ <i> Upbeat Music...</i>
